            "title": "Hibernation in bats (Mammalia: Chiroptera) did not evolve through positive selection of leptin",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Margaret E.",
                    "lastName": "Lazzeroni"
                },
                {
