            "title": "Second generation sequencing and morphological faecal analysis reveal unexpected foraging behaviour by Myotis nattereri (Chiroptera, Vespertilionidae) in winter",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Paul R",
